="zh-CN">为何祢却 忍耐着这一切</span></p><p begin="2:34.475" end="2:36.204" itunes:key="L52" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:34.475" end="2:34.730">¿Có</span><span begin="2:34.730" end="2:34.869">mo</span> <span begin="2:34.869" end="2:34.995">de</span><span begin="2:34.995" end="2:35.285">spe</span><span begin="2:35.285" end="2:35.424">jo</span> <span begin="2:35.424" end="2:35.565">mi</span> <span begin="2:35.565" end="2:35.789">men</span><span begin="2:35.821" end="2:36.204">te</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我该如何将思绪沉淀</span></p><p begin="2:36.512" end="2:38.432" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:36.512" end="2:36.560">Y</span> <span begin="2:36.560" end="2:36.602">a</span><span begin="2:36.664" end="2:36.882">pa</span><span begin="2:36.926" end="2:37.063">go</span> <span begin="2:37.063" end="2:37.178">el</span> <span begin="2:37.199" end="2:37.455">fue</span><span begin="2:37.495" end="2:37.630">go</span> <span begin="2:37.630" end="2:37.741">ar</span><span begin="2:37.760" end="2:37.914">di</span><span begin="2:37.914" end="2:38.040">en</span><span begin="2:38.040" end="2:38.432">te?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">才能压着燃起的火焰</span></p><p begin="2:47.829" end="2:49.772" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:47.829" end="2:48.086">Dear</span> <span begin="2:48.086" end="2:48.664">Lord,</span> <span begin="2:48.914" end="2:49.077">are</span> <span begin="2:49.077" end="2:49.263">you</span> <span begin="2:49.313" end="2:49.772">near?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">主啊 你要降临了吗？</span></p><p begin="2:53.452" end="2:54.860" itunes:key="L55" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:53.452" end="2:53.574">When</span> <span begin="2:53.574" end="2:53.741">are</span> <span begin="2:53.741" end="2:53.927">you</span> <span begin="2:53.927" end="2:54.132">com</span><span begin="2:54.132" end="2:54.281">ing</span> <span begin="2:54.321" end="2:54.607">ba</span><span begin="2:54.641" end="2:54.816">ck</span><span begin="2:54.816" end="2:54.860">?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">祢何时归来？</span></p></div></body></tt>